        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Imitation Firearms Safety Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill revises requirements related to imitation firearms, including by prohibiting a person from manufacturing, selling, shipping, transporting, or receiving an imitation firearm unless its exterior is brightly colored.</p>]]></text>
